text: MŠK Kysucké Nové Mesto is a Slovak football team, based in the town of Kysucké Nové Mesto. The club was founded in 1948. ==Honours== ===Domestic=== Czechoslovakia * 1.SNL (1st Slovak National football league) (1969–1993) ** Winners (1): 1972-73 == External links == *at sport.mkssknm.sk ==References== Kysucke Nove Mesto Category:Association football clubs established in 1948 Category:1948 establishments in Slovakia
